data.text:
PARTNERS IN ROUTE TO MARKET

PRTM a Broker-Distributor and Sales-Marketing Services Company.

PRTM, Partners in Route To Market, is a Broker, Distributor, Consultant, Sales & Marketing Services provider company focused on the Belgian, Dutch and Luxembourg Foodservice and Mass Retail Markets. We specialises in food and non-food consumer goods.

Partners in Route To Market vision is to act as your solution provider for your Brand & Product Development in the Benelux.

To ensure this goal PRTM has 3 core activities

The best Service you can get!
